'''SpaceX火星運輸系統'''（{{lang-en|SpaceX Mars Transportation System}}<REF name=name>
{{cite web|url=https://www.space.com/spacex-starship-super-heavy.html|title=Starship and Super Heavy: SpaceX's Mars-Colonizing Transportation System|work=Space.com|accessdate=16 January 2020|archive-date=2020-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200111092832/https://www.space.com/spacex-starship-super-heavy.html|dead-url=no}}
</REF>），是[[SpaceX|SpaceX]]的私人出资研发计划，以设计和建造一个用于火星殖民的太空飞行系统为目的。项目包括可重复使用[[运载火箭|运载火箭]]和[[太空飞船|太空飞船]]、地球上用于快速火箭发射与重新发射的基础设施、[[近地轨道|近地轨道]]推进剂加注系统、地外科技，最终用来实现[[火星殖民|火星殖民]]。这项技术也被设计成有能力支持以太阳系中其他地方为目的地的[[太空探索|太空探索任务]]，包括[[木星|木星]]和[[土星|土星]]的卫星<ref name="NYT-20160927">{{cite news |last=Chang |first=Kenneth |title=Elon Musk’s Plan: Get Humans to Mars, and Beyond |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/28/science/elon-musk-spacex-mars-exploration.html |date=27 September 2016 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |accessdate=27 September 2016 |archive-date=2016-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160929095051/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/09/28/science/elon-musk-spacex-mars-exploration.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。項目經過多次改名，之前被称作'''火星殖民运输器''' (Mars Colonial Transporter；MCT)，2016-17年稱為'''行星際運輸系統'''（Interplanetary Transport System；ITS）<ref name=ars20160918/>，2017年之後又改稱為'''大獵鷹火箭'''（Big Falcon Rocket；BFR）<REF>
{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tdUX3ypDVwI|title=Making Life Multiplanetary|publisher=|accessdate=16 January 2020|via=www.youtube.com|archive-date=2018-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180309212706/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tdUX3ypDVwI|dead-url=no}}
</REF>。2018年再將第二階段重新命名為'''[[SpaceX星艦|SpaceX星艦]]與超級重型'''（Starship and Super Heavy）<REF name=name/>。由於創辦人Elon Musk不斷改名，為了使本條目名稱更穩定，現一律統稱火星運輸系統。

SpaceX在2014年之前就开始了他们[[猛禽火箭发动机|猛禽火箭发动机]]的研发，到了2016年9月，SpaceX发布的遠程计划中<ref>{{cite news |url=http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/elon-musk-expected-detail-spacexs-mars-ambitions/story?id=42361304 |title=Elon Musk Expected to Detail SpaceX's Mars Ambitions |work=[[ABC_News|ABC News]] |date=2016-09-27 |accessdate=2016-09-27 |quote=''[Musk is] hoping for the first mission to Mars to take place around 2025.'' |archive-date=2016-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928153022/http://abcnews.go.com/Technology/elon-musk-expected-detail-spacexs-mars-ambitions/story?id=42361304 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，将先使用[[猎鹰重型运载火箭|猎鹰重型运载火箭]]发射两艘基于[[龙飞船|龙飞船]]的火星探测器，为今后星際探索任务作准备<ref name=gw20160128>{{cite news |last=Boyle |first=Alan |url=http://www.geekwire.com/2016/spacexs-elon-musk-wants-to-go-into-space-by-2021-and-start-sending-people-to-mars-by-2025/ |title=SpaceX’s Elon Musk wants to go into space by 2021 and start Mars missions by 2025 |work=GeekWire |date=2016-01-27 |accessdate=2016-01-29 |archive-date=2016-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160130084338/http://www.geekwire.com/2016/spacexs-elon-musk-wants-to-go-into-space-by-2021-and-start-sending-people-to-mars-by-2025/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；按照計畫，首次前往火星的ITS货运飞行不早于2022年，2024年將进行第一次载人ITS飞行<ref name=wapo20160613/> 。

==历史==
早在2007年，伊隆·马斯克就表示他个人的目标就是最终能让人类得以探索并殖民[[火星|火星]]<ref name=wired20070522>{{cite news|last=Hoffman|first=Carl|title=Elon Musk Is Betting His Fortune on a Mission Beyond Earth's Orbit|url=http://www.wired.com/science/space/magazine/15-06/ff_space_musk?currentPage=all|accessdate=2014-03-14|newspaper=Wired Magazine|date=2007-05-22|archive-date=2012-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114052527/http://www.wired.com/science/space/magazine/15-06/ff_space_musk?currentPage=all|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=mw20110422>{{cite news| title=Elon Musk: I'll Put a Man on Mars in 10 Years| url=http://www.marketwatch.com/video/asset/elon-musk-ill-put-a-man-on-mars-in-10-years-2011-04-22/CCF1FC62-BB0D-4561-938C-DF0DEFAD15BA#!CCF1FC62-BB0D-4561-938C-DF0DEFAD15BA| newspaper=Market Watch| date=2011-04-22| publisher=The Wall Street Journal| location=New York| accessdate=2011-12-01| archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/63bvaGo3E?url=http://www.marketwatch.com/video/asset/elon-musk-ill-put-a-man-on-mars-in-10-years-2011-04-22/CCF1FC62-BB0D-4561-938C-DF0DEFAD15BA#!CCF1FC62-BB0D-4561-938C-DF0DEFAD15BA| deadurl=no| archivedate=2011-12-01}}</ref> 
。关于登陸火星的計畫架構在2011到2015年间被陸陸續續揭露開來，其中一份2014年的声明表示最初的殖民者到达火星的时间不會早于2025年<ref name=dn20121213/>
，時至2016年年中，此項计划仍然把这一日期定为不早于2025年。<ref name=wapo20160613/>。

2011年，马斯克在一次采访中表示他希望在10~20年内把人类送上火星<ref name=mw20110422/>。 2012下半年，他表示他设想了一个人口达数万人的火星殖民地，而其中的殖民者到达火星的时间不早于2025年<ref name=dn20121213>{{cite news |url=http://news.discovery.com/space/alien-life-exoplanets/mars-colony-spacex-121126.htm |title=Huge Mars Colony Eyed by SpaceX Founder |date=2012-12-13 |accessdate=2014-03-14 |publisher=Discovery News |archive-date=2014-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141115083758/http://news.discovery.com/space/alien-life-exoplanets/mars-colony-spacex-121126.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=guardian20130717>{{cite news |last=Carroll |first=Rory |title=Elon Musk's mission to Mars |url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/jul/17/elon-musk-mission-mars-spacex |accessdate=2014-02-05 |newspaper=TheGuardian |date=2013-07-17 |archive-date=2014-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108024353/http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/jul/17/elon-musk-mission-mars-spacex |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=pa20140205>{{cite news |last=Messier |first=Doug |title=Elon Musk Talks ISS Flights, Vladimir Putin and Mars |url=http://www.parabolicarc.com/2014/02/05/elon-musk-interview-2/ |newspaper=Parabolic Arc |date=2014-02-05 |accessdate=2016-10-01 |archive-date=2018-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180916164003/http://www.parabolicarc.com/2014/02/05/elon-musk-interview-2/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2012年10月，马斯克构思了一个高层面上的有关建造第二套运载能力远超猎鹰九号与猎鹰重型的可重复使用火箭系统的计划，而SpaceX已经在原先的系统上花费了数十亿美元<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/spacex-aims-big-with-massive-new-rocket-377687/ |title=SpaceX aims big with massive new rocket |date=15 Oct 2012 |author=Zach Rosenberg |accessdate=2015-10-28 |publisher=Flight Global |archive-date=2015-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150703043710/http://www.flightglobal.com/news/articles/spacex-aims-big-with-massive-new-rocket-377687/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这款新运载火箭将会是对猎鹰九号火箭作出的的一次“演进”，而且将会大许多。但马斯克表示在2013年前SpaceX不会公开發表这项计划<ref name=dn20121213/><ref name=sdc20121123>{{cite news |last=Coppinger |first=Rod |title=Huge Mars Colony Eyed by SpaceX Founder Elon Musk |url=http://www.space.com/18596-mars-colony-spacex-elon-musk.html |accessdate=2013-06-10 |newspaper=Space.com |date=2012-11-23 |quote= -{an evolution of SpaceX's Falcon 9 booster ... much bigger [than Falcon 9], but I don’t think we’re quite ready to state the payload. We’ll speak about that next year. ... Vertical landing is an extremely important breakthrough — extreme, rapid reusability.}- |archive-date=2013-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130628154029/http://www.space.com/18596-mars-colony-spacex-elon-musk.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年6月，马斯克表示“在火星殖民运输器执行常规任务之前SpaceX不会进行[[首次公开募股|IPO]]”<ref name=forbes20130606>{{cite news |last=Schaefer |first=Steve |title=SpaceX IPO Cleared For Launch? Elon Musk Says Hold Your Horses |url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/steveschaefer/2013/06/06/with-tesla-and-solarcity-soaring-elon-musk-talks-down-spacex-ipo-plans/ |accessdate=2013-06-10 |newspaper=Forbes |date=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2013-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130609215317/http://www.forbes.com/sites/steveschaefer/2013/06/06/with-tesla-and-solarcity-soaring-elon-musk-talks-down-spacex-ipo-plans/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=tsdc20130606>{{cite news |last=Ciaccia |first=Chris |title=SpaceX IPO: 'Possible in the Very Long Term' |url=http://www.thestreet.com/story/11943630/1/spacex-ipo-possible-in-the-very-long-term.html |accessdate=2013-06-10 |newspaper=The Street |date=2013-06-06 |archive-date=2013-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130610064002/http://www.thestreet.com/story/11943630/1/spacex-ipo-possible-in-the-very-long-term.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年8月有媒体猜测，由[[猛禽火箭发动机|猛禽火箭发动机]]驱动的超重型运载火箭的首次飞行测试最早可在2020年进行，用以完全测试发动机在太空飞行环境下的表现；但是，所有殖民计划仍需漫長的等待<ref name=nbc20150105>{{cite news |last1=Boyle |first1=Alan |title=Coming Soon From SpaceX's Elon Musk: How to Move to Mars |url=http://www.nbcnews.com/science/space/coming-soon-spacexs-elon-musk-how-move-mars-n280311 |accessdate=8 January 2015 |work=NBC News |date=5 January 2015 |quote=''The Mars transport system will be a completely new architecture. Am hoping to present that towards the end of this year. Good thing we didn't do it sooner, as we have learned a huge amount from Falcon and Dragon.'' |archive-date=2015-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108064811/http://www.nbcnews.com/science/space/coming-soon-spacexs-elon-musk-how-move-mars-n280311 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=nsf20140830>{{cite news |last1=Bergin |first1=Chris |title=Battle of the Heavyweight Rockets -- SLS could face Exploration Class rival |url=http://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2014/08/battle-heavyweight-rockets-sls-exploration-rival/ |accessdate=2014-08-30 |publisher=NASAspaceflight.com |date=2014-08-29 |archive-date=2015-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316061403/http://www.nasaspaceflight.com/2014/08/battle-heavyweight-rockets-sls-exploration-rival/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年1月，马斯克说他希望在2015年末发表用于火星殖民的全新架构的细节。但这项计划有了变动，并在2015年12月时被挪到了2016年<ref name=gq20151212>{{cite news |last1=Heath |first1=Chris |title=How Elon Musk Plans on Reinventing the World (and Mars) |url=http://www.gq.com/story/elon-musk-mars-spacex-tesla-interview |accessdate=December 12, 2015 |work=GQ |date=December 12, 2015 |archive-date=2016-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818172215/http://www.gq.com/story/elon-musk-mars-spacex-tesla-interview |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年1月，马斯克表示他會在2016年9月的第67届国际宇航大会上描述SpaceX下一代火箭及飞船的火星任务的架构<ref name="musk@smuHK20160126">{{cite conference |title=2016 StartmeupHK Venture Forum - Elon Musk on Entrepreneurship and Innovation |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pIRqB5iqWA8 |conference=StartmeupHK Venture Forum--2016 |conferenceurl=http://www.startmeup.hk/en/startmeuphk-festival-2016/forum/ |publisher=Invest Hong Kong |place=via InvestHK YouTube channel |date=26 January 2016 |accessdate=28 January 2016 |quote=(SpaceX discussion at 30:15-31:40) ''We'll have the next generation rocket and spacecraft, beyond the Falcon and Dragon series ... I'm hoping to describe that architecture later this year at the International Astronautical Congress. which is the big international space event every year. ... first flights to Mars?  we're hoping to do that in around 2025 ... nine years from now or thereabouts.'' |archive-date=2016-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160128220018/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pIRqB5iqWA8 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.iac2016.org/ http://www.iac2016.org/] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iac2016.org/ |date=20160106204229 }}, accessed 28 January 2016.</ref><ref name=gw20160128/>。2016年6月，马斯克表示第一次无人火星殖民运输器的飞行计划于2022年出发，2024年的首次载人飞行紧随其后<ref name=wapo20160613>{{cite news |title=Elon Musk provides new details on his ‘mind blowing’ mission to Mars |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-switch/wp/2016/06/10/Elon-musk-provides-new-details-on-his-mind-blowing-mission-to-mars/ |work=[[Washington_Post|Washington Post]] |date=2016-06-13 |first=Christian |last=Davenport |accessdate=2016-06-14 |archive-date=2018-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180207180822/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/the-switch/wp/2016/06/10/elon-musk-provides-new-details-on-his-mind-blowing-mission-to-mars/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=gw20160610>{{cite news |last=Boyle |first=Alan |url=http://www.geekwire.com/2016/spacex-elon-musk-2024-mars-colony/ |title=SpaceX’s Elon Musk teases ‘dangerous’ plan to colonize Mars starting in 2024 |work=[[GeekWire|GeekWire]] |date=2016-06-10 |accessdate=2016-08-10 |archive-date=2016-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821102736/http://www.geekwire.com/2016/spacex-elon-musk-2024-mars-colony/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。大會上<ref name="musk@smuHK20160126"/>马斯克提到火星殖民运输器这一名字将不会延续，因为这套系统的能力“远不止火星”，并且将会有一个新名字：行星际运输系统<ref name=ars20160918>{{cite news |last=Berger |first=Eric |url=http://arstechnica.com/science/2016/09/spacexs-interplanetary-transport-system-will-go-well-beyond-mars/ |title=Elon Musk scales up his ambitions, considering going "well beyond" Mars |work=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]] |date=2016-09-18 |accessdate=2016-09-19 |archive-date=2016-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919001806/http://arstechnica.com/science/2016/09/spacexs-interplanetary-transport-system-will-go-well-beyond-mars/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。助推器直径为12米，飞船直径为17米，整个火箭组合体的高度为122米<ref name=nsf20140830/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/780831628104966144|title="12m rocket booster diameter, 17m spaceship diameter, 122 m stack height" - Elon Musk on Twitter|publisher=|accessdate=2016-10-01|archive-date=2016-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160927182509/https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/780831628104966144|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第一節將使用42台猛禽火箭发动机，起飛重量達到1萬500噸；第二級包含飛船本體，一樣使用[[猛禽火箭发动机|猛禽火箭发动机]]，也均採用液態甲烷、液氧作为燃料。<ref name=spacex-itspresentation201609>{{cite web |url=http://www.spacex.com/sites/spacex/files/mars_presentation.pdf |publisher=[[SpaceX|SpaceX]] |title=Making Humans a Multiplanetary Species |date=2016-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160928040332/http://www.spacex.com/sites/spacex/files/mars_presentation.pdf |archive-date=2016-09-28 |accessdate=2016-09-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>飛船出發前會在軌道上加注燃料，可搭載數百名乘員，在80天內抵達火星。另外飞船上還有兩片百萬瓦級太陽能板，以便供應電力。此計劃被命名為ITS。

次年，SpaceX的[[首席执行官|首席执行官]][[伊隆·马斯克|伊隆·马斯克]]在2017年的第68届[[国际宇航大会|国际宇航大会]]上宣佈ITS將改名為BFR，並展示了这个太空任务架构的细节，由於獵鷹系列的過時設計，行星系統的載具將會取代現有的火箭，這新型的火箭也將會執行所有的太空任務，此載具會用在與地球相關的航天活動上，另外也還有貨運版本。名稱將會為[[大猎鹰火箭|大猎鹰火箭]]，他表示尺寸稍微縮小了但火箭仍然非常大，有106米高，第一級改使用31部引擎。而跨行星際的載客船名稱為[[大猎鹰火箭#第二级/宇宙飞船：Starship（星舰）|星艦]]，直徑寬九米、長近48米，噸位達到1200噸，加壓艙大小將比目前的A380客機還大，有40間艙房，據稱共用活動空間也相當大，並能搭載150噸重的貨物到殖民地。同時也考量了太陽風暴而新設置了救生室。

2018年再度宣佈，第二期的BFR又被重新命名為Starship and Super Heavy。其中超級重型為第一期，星艦為第二期，預計於2023年達成。

